ratings.question_text: What is your overall assessment of this course?

narratives.question_text: How would you summarize AFAM 505 01/AMST 643 01 for a fellow student? Would you recommend AFAM 505 01/AMST 643 01 to another student? Why or why not?
comments: Great course, in a very important subject, so I consider this course a must take for any Computer Science student, and they can't find a better teacher to introduce them to the subject than Avi.

narratives.question_text: How did this course deepen your knowledge of your discipline/profession? To what extent did this course contribute to your dissertation/research?
comments: This course improved my knowledge on Databases, which will be helpful for the remaining of my career in Computer Science since Databases are apart of applications in most fields.
Useful for system design and web development.
